'''巴基斯坦国际航空公司PK661航班'''，在2016年12月7日在巴基斯坦的北部城市[[吉德拉爾|吉德拉爾]]飛往[[伊斯兰堡|伊斯兰堡]]時墜毀。失事客机机型为[[ATR_42|ATR 42-500]]，失事原因目前未明。<ref name=bbc>{{Cite web | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-38238699 | title = Pakistan International Airways flight 'crashes in north' | date = 2016-12-07 | accessdate = 2016-12-07 | publisher = BBC News | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161207132821/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-38238699 | archive-date = 2016-12-07 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name=reuters>{{Cite web | url = http://www.reuters.com/article/us-pakistan-airplane-idUSKBN13W1F5 | title = Pakistani plane with more than 40 people aboard crashes in north: police | publisher = Reuters | accessdate = 2016-12-07 | date = 2016-12-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161207122502/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-pakistan-airplane-idUSKBN13W1F5 | archive-date = 2016-12-07 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="dawn"/> 

==失事客机==
失事的[[ATR_42|ATR 42-500]]客机注册编号为AP-BHO<ref name=ah>{{Cite web | url = http://avherald.com/h?article=4a1c2ee4&opt=0 | publisher = [[The_Aviation_Herald|The Aviation Herald]] | date = 2016-12-07 | accessdate = 2016-12-07 | title = Crash: PIA AT42 near Abbottabad on Dec 7th 2016, engine problems | first = Simon | last = Hradecky | archive-date = 2018-11-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181116020357/http://avherald.com/h?article=4a1c2ee4&opt=0 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，2007年首飞并交付给巴基斯坦国际航空使用。2009年在一次降落在[[拉合爾|拉合爾]]的过程中受损，修复后继续服役。<ref>{{citeweb|title=ATR 42/72 – MSN 663 – AP-BHO|url=http://www.airfleets.net/ficheapp/plane-atr-663.htm|publisher=Airfleets|accessdate=2016-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161208121709/http://www.airfleets.net/ficheapp/plane-atr-663.htm|archive-date=2016-12-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 航班資料 ==
当地时间15:30，飞机离开{{link-en|吉德拉爾機場|Chitral Airport}}，预计于16:40分抵达[[伊斯兰堡|伊斯兰堡]][[贝娜齐尔·布托国际机场|贝娜齐尔·布托国际机场]]<ref name="dawn">{{cite news|url=https://www.rt.com/document/5847fd52c46188b94e8b458f/amp|title=PIA flight #PK661 crashes, 'bodies burned beyond recognition'|last=|first=|date=2016-12-07|work=RT|via=|accessdate=2016-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161210074300/https://www.rt.com/document/5847fd52c46188b94e8b458f/amp|archive-date=2016-12-10|dead-url=no}}</ref> 飞机失事之前，机组曾发出[[Mayday|Mayday]]求救信号。<ref name="thenews">{{cite web|title=PIA plane crashes near Abbottabad, all passengers feared dead|url=https://www.thenews.com.pk/latest/170426-PIA-plane-crashed-near-Abbottabad|publisher=[[卡拉奇新闻报|卡拉奇新闻报]]|accessdate=2016-12-07|date=|website=The News|last=|first=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161207131411/https://www.thenews.com.pk/latest/170426-PIA-plane-crashed-near-Abbottabad|archive-date=2016-12-07|dead-url=no}}</ref> 飞机在16:15左右坠毁，残骸散布在在开伯尔-普赫图赫瓦省赫韦利扬[[巴基斯坦兵工厂|巴基斯坦兵工厂]]附近的一座山上，距首都约90千米。<ref name="AP08-12-16">{{cite news|url=http://www.newser.com/article/f2cd537617c14880afd7783ed635dace/pakistan-opens-probe-into-deadly-plane-crash-that-killed-47.html|title=Pakistan opens probe into deadly plane crash that killed 47|agency=Associated Press|last1=Shahzad|first1=Asif|last2=Ahmed|first2=Munir|date=2016-12-08|accessdate=2016-12-08|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161208141114/http://www.newser.com/article/f2cd537617c14880afd7783ed635dace/pakistan-opens-probe-into-deadly-plane-crash-that-killed-47.html|archivedate=2016-12-08}}</ref>据一名目击者说，飞机坠毁前高度很低，发出高频噪音并且时而爬升时而下降。<ref name="Dawn08-12-16">{{cite news|url=https://www.dawn.com/news/1301192/nation-in-grief-over-airliner-tragedy|title=Nation in grief over airliner tragedy|work=Dawn|first1=Rashid|last1=Javed|first2=Manzoor|last2=Ali|date=2016-12-08|accessdate=2016-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161208124955/http://www.dawn.com/news/1301192/nation-in-grief-over-airliner-tragedy|archive-date=2016-12-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>

当地清真寺用广播动员附近居民参加救援，不过由于温度过高，村民无法接近飞机残骸。<ref name="Dawn08-12-16" />巴基斯坦陆军也派出士兵与直升机展开搜索救援行动。一名政府官员称，所有的遗体都已经被大火烧得面目全非，无法辨认。<ref name=dawn/> 乘客遗体会被空运到伊斯兰堡和拉瓦尔品第，那里的法医实验室会对他们进行DNA测试以确定死者身份。<ref name="AP08-12-16" />

==乘客==
机上共有5名机组人员，1名地面工程师。乘客中包括40名成人以及2名婴儿。<ref name="PIA_Official" />其中四十四名是巴基斯坦公民; 其余有两个奥地利人和一个中国人。

